# v0.1.12_Recipe_Header_Operational

## Summary

This release establishes a stable operational Recipe Header workflow and resolves the save/load issues that appeared when Yield Qty and Yield Unit were introduced.

Recipe Components have not yet started. This milestone focuses solely on Recipe Header functionality and Recipe workspace stability.

