---

## Propagation Rule Confirmed

Nothing propagates downstream until Save.

After Save:

* Saved recipe state becomes authoritative
* Saved recipe cost automatically updates downstream usages
* Unsaved edits remain local to the open workspace

Sub-recipes follow the same rule.

Saved state propagates.
Unsaved state does not.

